  "instructions": [
    "Mix together rice and water in a large bowl until the rice is fully soaked.",
    "Add coconut milk, yeast, sugar, and salt, and mix until combined.",
    "Cover the bowl with a cloth and let it rest for 2 hours.",
    "Preheat oven to 375\u00133F (190\u00133C).",
    "Prepare terracotta dishes by sprinkling a small amount of salt inside each one.",
    "Pour the rice mixture into the prepared dishes, about 2/3 full.",
    "Bake in the preheated oven for 30 minutes, or until the rice is cooked through and the tops are golden brown.",
    "Remove from the oven and brush with a little vegetable oil.",
    "Sprinkle with sesame seeds and a pinch of salt, and serve warm.",
    "Serve immediately, garnished with a slice of lime and a sprinkle of lime zest.",
    "Enjoy your delicious Khanom Krok!"
  ],
